shorturi is a URL-shortening python module which supports the following URL shortening services:

  * goo.gl
  * is.gd
  * cli.gs

Support for more URL-shortening services will be added soon.

This package also includes a script 'shorturi' which invokes the python module for shortening URIs.

To install the python module and the shorturi script, run this command as root from the source root dir:

python setup.py install


